xyz.fsgik.common.convert

接口 FsConverter.Options

  • 封闭接口:
    FsConverter

    public static interface FsConverter.Options
    Options for conversion.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明
      static class  FsConverter.Options.Builder
      Builder for FsConverter.Options.

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      static int NO_REUSE
      Policy value for object reuse: Never return the source object if the source object is not immutable.
      static int REUSE_ASSIGNABLE
      Policy value for object reuse: If and only if target type is assignable from source type, return the source object.
      static int REUSE_EQUAL
      Policy value for object reuse: If and only if target type is equal to source type, return the source object.

    • 方法概要

      Returns an Options of which reusePolicy() is replaced by given policy.

      Returns options with given object reuse policy.

    • 字段详细资料

      • REUSE_ASSIGNABLE

        static final int REUSE_ASSIGNABLE
        Policy value for object reuse:
        • If and only if target type is assignable from source type, return the source object.
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值

      • REUSE_EQUAL

        static final int REUSE_EQUAL
        Policy value for object reuse:
        • If and only if target type is equal to source type, return the source object.
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值

      • NO_REUSE

        static final int NO_REUSE
        Policy value for object reuse:
        • Never return the source object if the source object is not immutable. If the source object is immutable, it may still be returned.
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值
